		<a href="/docs/api/lithium/2.0.x/lithium" class="symbol-segment">lithium</a>\<a href="/docs/api/lithium/2.0.x/lithium/security" class="symbol-segment">security</a>\<a href="/docs/api/lithium/2.0.x/lithium/security/Password" class="symbol-segment">Password</a>::hash()		</h1>

		<section class="under">
